  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 6, then take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Cut the <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into thin fries</p><p>Add the <strong>fries</strong> to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray with a drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong>, give everything a good mix up and put the tray in the oven for 20-25 min or until crispy</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1605106772589-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1605106772589-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1605106772589-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1605106772589-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1605106772589-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the fries are in the oven, cut the <strong>chicken breast portions </strong>into strips</p><p>Add the <strong>chicken strips</strong>, <strong>soy sauce </strong>and <strong>smoked paprika</strong> to a bowl and give everything a good mix up then set aside</p><p>Add the <strong>cornflour </strong>and <strong>dried oregano</strong> to a shallow plate with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong> and mix well – this is your <strong>herby flour mix</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1605106784507-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1605106784507-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
