    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the <strong>chicken strips</strong> from the bowl and firmly press each one into the <strong>herby flour mix</strong>,<strong> </strong>making sure to evenly coat them on both sides – these are your <strong>coated chicken strips</strong></p>",
