    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a very generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> (enough to cover the base of the pan) over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> coated chicken strips</strong> and cook for 4-5 min on each side or until golden brown, crispy and cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your<strong> crispy fried chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
