    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> (not a fan of raw garlic? Go easy!) with the <strong>mayo</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> water and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>in a small bowl – this is your <strong>garlic mayo</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> in a separate bowl – this is your <strong>salad dressing</strong></p>",
