    {
      "instruction": "<p>Spread your <strong>warmed brioche buns</strong> with the<strong> garlic mayo</strong>, then pile up the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong> and<strong> crispy fried chicken </strong>on top</p><p>Serve the<strong> fries</strong>,<strong> diced tomato</strong> and <strong>remaining shredded lettuce </strong>to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>salad dressing </strong>over the<strong> tomato</strong> and lettuce</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
